page.title: 06A TYPICAL DAY...1
page.content: AT 6.30 AM I WAKE UP AND READ.AT 7.30 AM I GET UP AND DRESS AND I ALSO CHECK MY SCHOOL BAG.AFTER THAT I GO AND HAVE MY BREAKFAST AND MY FRIEND CALLS FOR ME.WE THEN WALK TO SCHOOL. I THEN LEAVE MY FLUTE IN THE MUSIC ROOM AND I CHAT IN THE HALLWAY. WE THEN HAVE REGISTRATION AND ASSEMBLY.THEN OUR FIRST LESSON, AFTER WHICH IS BREAK AND THEN OUR SECOND LESSON.WE THEN HAVE LUNCHTIME AND A CLUB.THEN REGISTRATION AND THIRD LESSON.THEN BREAK AND LESSON FOUR. I THEN GO HOME AT 4PM,I WALK HOME AND GO INTO THE SWEET SHOP FOR SWEETS. WHEN I GET HOME I GET CHANGED AND WATCH TELEVISION. AFTER TEA I DO MY HOMEWORK AND PRACTICE MY FLUTE AND PIANO. I THEN GO OUT TO ADVENTURERS. AFTER THE ADVENTURERS I GO AND GET UNDRESSED AND GO TO BED.
